title: The Refugees.S01E04-06.720p.HDTV.x264_TTL
description:
All credit to the original caper on both the files that I used here.									

																

This has been remuxed from 2 sources(skgtv 720p which had an unvalid sound file that would not play in VLC or a stand alone 

Bluray player and  their non 720p cap which had a valid sound file).									

																 

I added chapters since I was doing all this work and I have added my logo because I was not sure whether to call it a Proper or a 

Repack, so I called it neither.														

																	

Grab the sample and if you like it go for it.												

																	

Enjoy and please share
